  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC264">
          <l>maṟṟaiya teṉṉuṅ kiḷavi tāṉē</l>
          <l>cuṭṭunilai yoḻiya viṉaṅkuṟit taṉṟē.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/164/mode/1up">164</ref>.</p>
      <p>
pala pottakam kiṭantavaḻi, oruvaṉ ēvalāḷaṉaip pārttup, ‘pottakaṅ koṇṭuvā’ eṉṟāl, avaṉ oru pottakaṅ koṇṭuvantaviṭattut tāṉ karutiya pottakam aṉṟeṉil,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘maṟṟaiyatu koṇā’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṉum; eṉṟakkāl, ikkoṇarntataṉai yoḻikkuñ col ik koṇarnta pottakam cuṭṭiṟṟākalāṉ, koṇarntataṉai oḻikkuñ cuṭṭunilai ataṉai yoḻittu oḻintateṉṟu avviṉattallatu piṟitoṉṟu kuṟittatu kollō eṉiṟ kuṟiyā; maṟṟu ap pottakattuḷ piṉṉuṅ kuṟittatu eṉappaṭum.    (16)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n214/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n215/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. maṟṟaiyateṉap peyarkku mutaṉilaiyāy varum maṟṟaiyeṉṉum aikāravīṟ ṟiṭaiccol, cuṭṭappaṭṭataṉai oḻittu, ataṉiṉaṅkuṟittu niṟkum. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
āṭai koṇarntavaḻi avvāṭai vēṇṭātāṉ
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Cena-cit1">
        <l>maṟṟaiyatu koṇā</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
veṉṉum. aḵtu accuṭṭiyavāṭaiyoḻittu ataṟkiṉa mākiya piṟavāṭai kuṟittu niṉṟavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka.
      </p>
      <p>
perumpāṉmaiyum mutaṉilaiyāy niṉṟallatu avviṭaiccoṟporuḷ viḷakkāmaiyiṉ, ‘maṟṟaiyateṉṉuṅkiḷavi’ yeṉṟār. ciṟupāṉmai
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Cena-cit2">
        <l>maṟṟaiyāṭai</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉat tāṉēyum varum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Cena-cit3">
        <l>maṟṟaiyaḵtu,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Cena-cit4">
        <l>maṟṟaiyavaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṉuntoṭakkattaṉavum avviṭaiccoṉmutaṉilaiyāya peyar.  (16)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/294/mode/1up">294</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/295/mode/1up">295</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i–ḷ) maṟṟaiya teṉṉuṅ kiḷavitāṉē – maṟṟaiyateṉap peyarkku mutaṉilaiyāy varum maṟṟaiyeṉṉumai kāra vīṟṟiṭaiccol, cuṭṭunilai yoḻiya viṉaṅkuṟit taṉṟē ― oruvaṉ muṉṉark karutappaṭṭa poruḷoḻiya vataṉiṉap poruḷaik karuti niṟku meṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u–m) āṭai koṇarntavaḻi, yavvāṭai vēṇṭātār,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘maṟṟaiyatu koṇṭu vā’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
veṉṟāl, ataṟkiṉamākiya piṟavāṭai kuṟittu niṟkum iṉic ciṟupāṉmai
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘maṟṟai āṭai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
yeṉat tāṉēyum varum.
      </p>
      <p>
aḵtu, avaṉeṉṉun toṭakkattaṉa vaṟṟiṟku
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Nacc-cit3">
        <l>maṟṟai yaḵtu,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Nacc-cit4">
        <l>‘maṟṟaiyavaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa avviṭaiccol mutal nilaiyāy varutaliṉ maṟṟaiyeṉa iṭaiccollaip pirittu ōtātu maṟṟaiyatu eṉa oṉṟāka ōtiṉār.
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n181/mode/1up">174</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
i–ḷ: ― maṟṟaiyatu eṉṉuñ col cuṭṭi niṉṟa poruḷ oḻiya ataṟkiṉamākiya poruḷaikkuṟittu niṟkum. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
atu eṉpatu evvāṟu vantatu eṉiṉ, mēl viṉaimāṟṟu eṉṟār, itu poruṇmai māṟṟu eṉpataṉai viḷakkutaṟku atu eṉpataṉaik kūṭṭiyuraittār. atu eṉpatu peyarātaliṉ
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Tey-cit1">
        <l>orupāṟkiḷavi eṉaippāṟ kaṇṇum–varuvatāmē vaḻakkeṉa moḻipa<note place="foot">poruḷiyal. 28</note></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpataṉāṉ aintupāṟkaṇṇum koḷka. avvāṟu koḷḷavē, maṟṟai eṉpatu iṭaiccollāki niṉṟu piṟaporuḷuṇarttiyavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉaṅkuṟittu eṉṟamaiyāṟ, cuṭṭappaṭṭa poruṭku iṉamākiya poruḷaiyē kuṟikkum. āṭai koṇarntavaḻi,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Tey-cit2">
        <l>maṟṟaiyatō</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉiṟ, koṇarntatoḻiyap piṟitumōrāṭaiyaic cuṭṭiyavāṟu kaṇṭu koḷka. oru viṉaiceyvār iruvaruḷvaḻi, oruvaṉaikkaṇṭavaṉ
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC264-Tey-cit3">
        <l>maṟṟaiyavaṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻi, atuvum iṉaṅkuṟittatu. piṟavumaṉṉa.	[16]
      </p>
    </body>
